bilingual.source: The chicken is between the fence posts.
The post box was next to the fence post.
He likes to jump over the fence.
The old fence was missing a stave.
The child was peeping over the fence.

list.abstract: fence，英 [fens]，美 [fens]。英语单词，作名词时，指的是篱笆；栅栏。作动词时，指的是用篱围住；买卖；击剑；搪塞；兜圈子。短句搭配为“electric fence（电篱笆）”。例句为“The fence had had three coats of paint.（篱笆上已经涂了三层漆）”。 fence近义词为bounding wall，perimeter wall。

yingyinNormal.en: All right! Fence mended, problem swept under the rug. Time to bowl!
yingyinNormal.zh: 太好了，栅栏已补，误会已清，去打保龄球吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny and Candy are hiding in the branches of a little tree. Zoe, Pedro and Rebecca are hiding behind a fence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼和坎迪藏到了小树的树枝后面。苏怡，佩德罗和瑞贝卡藏到了栅栏后面。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny and Candy are hiding in the branches of a little tree. Zoe, Pedro and Rebecca are hiding behind a fence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼和坎迪藏到了小树的树枝后面。苏怡，佩德罗和瑞贝卡藏到了栅栏后面。

yingyinNormal.en: The balance of which involved spying over her back fence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们偷偷溜去她家后院。

yingyinNormal.en: Leadership, guarding the fence, or keeping the factionless from killing each other.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做领导者，做守城墙的哨兵，还是阻止无派系的乞丐们自相残杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you really think that we wanted to drive through a fence? Can you just have Dad come and…
yingyinNormal.zh: 难道是我们想让车撞上篱笆的吗？你能让爸爸过来…

yingyinNormal.en: He's struggling, Dom. He doesn't want me to see it, but the white picket fence is like an anchor for him. I can tell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他很纠结，多姆，他不想让我看到但我能看的出来，这种平淡的家庭生活对他来说是牵绊。

yingyinNormal.en: Out there, beyond that fence, every living thing that crawls, flies or squats in the mud wants to kill you and eat your eyes for Jujubes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这道围栏外面，所有地上爬的，天上飞的，土里钻的生物都想要弄死你，再把你眼珠子挖出来当枣吞了。

yingyinNormal.en: In 1931, Thomas Edison confided to his friend, Henry Ford, "we are like tenant farmers, chopping down the fence around our house for fuel, when we should be using nature's inexhaustible sources of energy, sun, wind, and tide."
yingyinNormal.zh: 1931年，托马斯·爱迪生悄悄告诉他的朋友亨利·福特"，我们就像土地租用人，当我们需要时，砍我们房子周边的篱笆做燃料，自然就是取之不尽用之不竭的能源，太阳，风和潮水"。
